The paper presents a method for integrating image-based measurements into a drone navigation system for the automated inspection of wind turbines. This involves using a convolutional neural network for image processing and a pose graph optimiser for estimating 3D pose. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
